    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3, preserved in concours condition. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system that operates with surgical precision. The chassis remains structurally flawless with documented subframe reinforcement and factory-spec bushings. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock. The exterior retains its factory depth with zero oxidation, while the underside remains free of any thermal cycling fatigue. Recent Blackstone oil reports confirm optimal rod bearing health, ensuring this high-revving masterpiece performs exactly as it did when it rolled off the Dingolfing assembly line.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
